  <summary date="2007-03-20T18:42:27Z" status="Introduced in House">Save Our Shores Act - Amends the Harmful Algal Bloom and Hypoxia Research and Control Act of 1998 to extend the authorization of appropriations for research, education, and monitoring activities related to the prevention, reduction, and control of harmful algal blooms and hypoxia.

Requires that all federal financial assistance for harmful algal bloom research be awarded on a competitive, peer reviewed basis.</summary>
